%N A290492 Maximal number of binary vectors of length n such that the unions (or bitwise ORs) of any 3 distinct vectors are all distinct.
%C A290492 Maximal number of subsets of an n-set such that the unions of any 3 distinct subsets are all distinct.
%C A290492 The concatenation of these vectors produces a 3-separable matrix.
